{"tid":2297502,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚晚 黑心黃店悪の$52咖喱瀏覽焗飯","createTime":"2020-11-23T10:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T04:51:46.000Z","uid":13361,"like":74,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d82fe207a3b7224c00fce3377685158a27b72852","tid":2297502,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcPhvxC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmcPhvxC.jpg&h=1cf28157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瀏覽有7/8舊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />牛筋有4舊 有啲爽口有啲就好淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有啲炸薯仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 默認炒飯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夠乾身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />餸多過飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成本應該唔洗$10 賣貴五倍 黑店fced <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外仲聽到老闆娘同廚房佬屌政府 小妹嘅愛國心好唔c服<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b52fd39bc67372c221beead9dd804c13caf32e4","tid":2297502,"uid":141668,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭，拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43f8332382d4563f71e75caf53fe79d4246041f","tid":2297502,"uid":244451,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"$52咁足料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪用左黑心牛肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我去試下佢乜料先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 